n  border: 1px solid var(--line);\n  border-radius: 10px;\n  padding: 9px 10px;\n  width: 100%;\n  color: inherit;\n  background: #fff;\n}\n/* No focus styles currently */\n```\n\n## Section 5 — Existing Tests\n\nNo CSS-specific tests exist. This is a pure CSS change with no backend impact.\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
