rizmClaw\n- LANG: nodejs\n- No CSS-specific module doc needed (pure frontend CSS change)\n\nCSS Variables in :root:\n- --primary: #3a6ff7\n- --line: #dfe3ef\n\n## Section 4 — Existing Source Files\n\n### public/styles.css (265 lines)\n\n```css\n:root {\n  color-scheme: light;\n  --bg: #f4f6fb;\n  --panel: #ffffff;\n  --line: #dfe3ef;\n  --text: #1f2633;\n  --muted: #667085;\n  --primary: #3a6ff7;\n  --primary-contrast: #ffffff;\n  --warning: #d97706;\n  --danger: #b42318;\n  --chat-user: #e9f0ff;\n  --chat-assistant: #f5f7fa;\n  --radius: 12px;\n}\n\n/* ... existing styles ... */\n\ninput,\ntextarea {\n  border: 1px solid var(--line);\n  border-radius: 10px;\n  padding: 9px 10px;\n  width: 100%;\n  color: inherit;\n  background: #fff;\n}\n/* No focus styles currently */\n```\n\n## Section 5 — Existing Tests\n\nNo CSS-specific tests exist. This is a pure CSS change with no backend impact.\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":61,"oldLines":6,"newStart":61,"newLines":11,"lines":[" /* No focus styles currently */"," ```"," ","-## Section 5 — Existing Tests","+## Implementation Log","+Files changed/created:","+- public/styles.css — added `input:focus, textarea:focus` block after line 103"," ","-No CSS-specific tests exist. This is a pure CSS change with no backend impact.","+Key decisions:","+- Used `rgba(58, 111, 247, 0.18)` (hardcoded alpha of --primary) for box-shadow since CSS custom properties can't be used directly in rgba() without color-mix or CSS Color Level 4","+- `outline: none` ensures no double-outline in any browser","+- `border-color: var(--primary)` reinforces focus state visually with primary color"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
